  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2965541/" class="title-link">喜欢读书的人都应该去看看</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2965541"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/30858637/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/30858637/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">长剑</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-01-30"
      class="main-meta">2010-01-30 13:08:18</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2965541_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  五年前在大学读法律时，就比较喜欢读一些哲学书籍，当时就有这本西方哲学原著选读的上下本，那个时候读就是一种增加阅历的目的，提升人得思想，直到今天，和别人谈起这些知识时，感觉自己当初要是没有读的话，就不会有今天的收获。

