  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5363692/" class="title-link">人类的大宗师、哲学始祖苏格拉底（Socrates）</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5363692"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/sahaja/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u42033941-7.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/sahaja/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">公益霎哈嘉瑜伽</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar20 main-title-rating" title="较差"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-03-28"
      class="main-meta">2012-03-28 09:35:00</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5363692_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  苏格拉底（Socrates，前469——前399年）被后人广泛认为是西方哲学的奠基者。苏氏出身平民，生活刻苦，他以自学成为一名很有学问的人，30多岁时做了一名不取报酬也不设馆的社会道德教师，许多青年常常聚集在他周围，向他请教。他平易近人，热情洋溢，具有朴实的语言，加之幽默...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 7没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5363692_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5363692_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





